{"tid":2328541,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消息指5名警員曾接觸李偲嫣　有機會要檢測","createTime":"2020-12-16T15:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T17:10:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0362c8acb4d0bd9fd14c2511d312d5e4db2e91c6","tid":2328541,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T15:10:07.000Z","msg":"消息指，八鄉警署5名警員，曾接觸已離世的正義聯盟發起人李偲嫣，5人需要在警署其中一間房等待指示，有機會要到醫院檢測，或需要隔離至有檢測結果。據了解，李偲嫣今日由救護車送往博愛醫院，在急症室不治，對新型肺炎病毒測試，呈初步陽性。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，涉事5名警員接觸有關患者時，只戴上口罩，沒有其他防護裝備，正等待衛生署進一步指示，警署其他人員現時毋須檢測或隔離，八鄉警署運作正常。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565682-20201216.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565682-20201216.htm&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE18emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=a5dee05c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565682-20201216.htm&h=8ba45489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565682-20201216.htm</a>"},{"pid":"953ebdbdf663cb8c496ac983150f15452ad0513b","tid":2328541,"uid":8572,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T15:10:40.000Z","msg":"召妓群組？"},{"pid":"425cc9ea131c829e6e69b0cee3298c7a63e3b943","tid":2328541,"uid":226955,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T15:10:53.000Z","msg":"最後嘅禮物"},{"pid":"c972b2cc80115a21943de095c74d1e3c29400dc8","tid":2328541,"uid":15211,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T15:11:24.000Z","msg":"李漢民千祈唔好有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0074fdcfb6ea45a92c2bdf2a3b462d7c691984","tid":2328541,"uid":310867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T15:11:46.000Z","msg":"毒婦（武肺）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d3c7c8e0296984c22bdb39149